OL,3,CAirport delays improve in Isle of Man
OL,4,Cbut air traffic control remains big
OL,5,Cissue
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports' Isle of Man
OL,8,Freporter Joshua Stokes has the latest.
OL,10,FFrequent flyers in the Isle of Man are
OL,11,Fno strangers to the challenge of
OL,12,Fgetting on and off the island.
OL,14,FOver the last couple of years, air
OL,15,Ftravel has become harder across Europe
OL,16,Fdue to a number of different factors.
