OL,3,CAirport delays improve in Isle of Man
OL,4,Cbut air traffic control remains big
OL,5,Cissue
OL,7,FAn increased demand in overseas
OL,8,Fholidays, a shortage of staff and
OL,9,Fvarious strikes across the continent
OL,10,Fhas all contributed to the post-Covid
OL,11,Fdisruption.
OL,13,FOn the Isle of Man, that disruption is
OL,14,Foften felt strongly by its people,
OL,15,Frelying on just one airport to fly.
OL,17,FAn airport smaller in size, operating
OL,18,Ffrom the middle of the Irish Sea, and
OL,19,Ftherefore prone to changeable weather
OL,20,Fconditions, with a minimal pool of
OL,21,Ftrained staff.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
