OL,7,FAs a result, Ronaldsway Airport is
OL,8,Fforced to close its runway on two
OL,9,Fseparate occasions during the day, to
OL,10,Ffacilitate regulated breaks for its
OL,11,Fair traffic control officers (ATCOs).
OL,13,FA lack of trained staff means the
OL,14,Fairport is unable to operate during
OL,15,Fall working hours.
