OL,3,CAirport delays improve in Isle of Man
OL,4,Cbut air traffic control remains big
OL,5,Cissue
OL,7,FHead of Air Traffic Services, Geoff
OL,8,FPugh, said: "We time those (breaks) to
OL,9,Fdeconflict with the scheduled
OL,10,Foperations as far as we can, but of
OL,11,Fcourse if an aircraft then doesn't
OL,12,Farrive on time for whatever reason,
OL,13,Fthat can obviously add complexity to
OL,14,Fthat.
OL,16,F"We can certainly add to those delays,
OL,17,Fbut in the vast majority of cases we
OL,18,Fare not the cause of the delays."
