OL,4,Cbut air traffic control remains big
OL,5,Cissue
OL,7,FA shortage of ATCOs is a problem faced
OL,8,Fby a number of different airports
OL,9,Facross Europe.
OL,11,FSince the Covid-19 pandemic, there has
OL,12,Fbeen an increase in the number of
OL,13,Fpeople travelling abroad for holidays,
OL,14,Fputting further strain on the ATC
OL,15,Fsystem.
OL,17,FIt takes an average of three years to
OL,18,Ffully train an ATCO, with a higher
OL,19,Frisk of failure than most roles.
