OL,4,Cbut air traffic control remains big
OL,5,Cissue
OL,7,FRonaldsway needs 18 trained ATCOs to
OL,8,Fbe fully operational, and it currently
OL,9,Fhas 16.
OL,11,FAccording to statistics held by the
OL,12,Fairport, a quarter of all flights were
OL,13,Fdelayed between January and July.
OL,15,FOut of 2775 flights departing
OL,16,FRonaldsway, 707 were delayed by 16
OL,17,Fminutes or more.
