OL,4,Cbut air traffic control remains big
OL,5,Cissue
OL,7,FHowever, this is an improvement
OL,8,Fcompared to the 936 flights that were
OL,9,Fdelayed in 2023 across the same time
OL,10,Fperiod.
OL,12,FCommercial Director, Hannah Lo Bao
OL,13,Fsaid: "With delays it all comes down
OL,14,Fto the airlines having the resilience
OL,15,Fin their aircraft - it's getting
OL,16,Fbetter - so lots of them are seeing
OL,17,Fimprovements in the data like we have.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
