OL,7,F"But yeah, we're all still a little
OL,8,Fbit vulnerable and I think probably
OL,9,Ffor the next couple of summers you'll
OL,10,Fstill see some of that vulnerability."
OL,12,FStaff have, however, announced
OL,13,Fimprovements across the airport, which
OL,14,Finclude plans for new facilities,
OL,15,Fincluding an extension to the current
OL,16,Fbar and Costa Coffee in the departure
OL,17,Flounge.
